name: naphthalen-2-yl-acetonitrile
Reason: 1,2-propanediol base melting point around 50 degrees Celsius, based on the fact that 1,2-propanediol itself has a melting point around that value. The naphthalene ring introduces a significant increase due to the rigidity and molecular weight. Each naphthalene ring may contribute around +20 to +30°C.
